These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis, poppy, dahlia
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, red, turquise, yellow
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the owner of the horse is the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Flower   | amaryllis       | marigold | poppy     | dahlia    |
| Color   | yellow | red         | mauve  | turquise    |
| Pet           | horse      | mouse       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

