.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, april, september
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, collecting, baking, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Birthday      | may      | november     | april    | september |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| Hobby           | dancing         | collecting | baking     | photography        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

