.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, french
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, rock, punk, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, sunflower, iris, rose
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the fan of disco##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person who growsrose is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the french is the fan of rock##1
10. the british is on the left of the fan of punk##1
11. the person who growsrose is on the left of the fan of punk##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Music-Genre           | rock       | pop         | disco  | punk         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| Flower     | iris       | daffodil         | rose   | sunflower        |

