.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, trance, punk, funk
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, japanese, thai
4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, billiard, whist
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, taxi, trike
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Music-Genre          | punk     | folk   | funk | trance |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Game           | bridge       | backgammon      | whist     | billiard |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | taxi     | trike     | roller     |

