4 different games are played: domino, billiard, monopoly, bridge
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, metal, rock, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
 4. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking water is the fan of rock##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is the person drinking water##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | water     | juice      | soy-milk    | 7up           |
| City         | liverpool   | prague  | hannover  | rome |
