 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes grey##1
10. the person drinking water is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| City         | liverpool  | berlin | prague | london |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Color   | grey     | turquise     | red       | green          |

