.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, satire, mystery, epic
House: futuristic, cottage, victorian, wooden
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, goldfish, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the wooden house is the person watching western movies##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the wooden house is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the cottage house##1
 8. the futuristic house is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person eating grapes is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre       | mystery       | western       | satire      | epic |
| House         | cottage | wooden | victorian | futuristic      |
| Pet         | cat          | snake         | goat           | goldfish    |
| Transport   | ship         | scooter       | snowmobile     | motorbike   |

 